strings.description: YouthMappers chapter at Universidade Eduardo Mondlane
strings.extendedDescription: We are a student group that intends to join Mozambican society to create a resilient community of humanitarian mapping. The community intend to map the physical occupation of our Country and create open geographic data, accessible to the public and able to be used in several areas without associated costs.
